===Glyph origin===
Graphical manipulations on {{zh-l|兵|[[soldier]]}}.

===Etymology===
A similar-sounding onomatopoeia to the source character {{zh-l|兵|[[soldier]]}}. First attested in {{w|Ming Dynasty}} and referred to the sound of collisions (for example, in ''Journey to the West''). Later used as a translation of {{der|zh|en|ping pong}}.

